oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gerard Purcell Assoc. Job No. 37813
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2383) for an order placed for Gerard Purcell Association by Eddie Cummings for 300 one color window cards for a performance of the Al Hert Show at the Nashville Municipal Auditorium on February 25. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
